OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late brightness.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will be
OL,8,Flargely dry but some rain spreading
OL,9,Finto Galloway later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FOutbreaks of rain will
OL,12,Fspread east across all parts during
OL,13,Fthe morning. Then bright spells and
OL,14,Fscattered showers following on for the
OL,15,Fafternoon. Colder than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
